T1  - The distribution of welfare gains from price stabilization: An international perspective
AU  - Just, Richard
AU  - Lutz, Ernst
AU  - Schmitz, Andrew
AU  - Turnovsky, Stephen
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 8
IS  - 4
SP  - 551
